title: David Bowie - 1997-01-09 - Save the Children
description:
This is a very nice David Bowie concert. Check my account for more Bowie stuff.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Artist: David Bowie

Date: January 09, 1997

Title: "Save the Children"

Label: Optimum  (01/02)

Source: Digital Soundboard Recording

Venue: Madison Square Garden, New York, New York

Other: 50th Birthday Benefit Concert featuring Frank Black, Foo Fighters, Robert Smith, Sonic Youth, Lou Reed and Billy Corgan.
            	    
Lineage: DVB-C > CDr > EAC > WAV > FLAC [level 8]

Size: 929 MB

Lineup: David Bowie, vocals, guitar and keyboards; Reeves Gabrels, guitar; Mike Garson, keyboards; Gail Ann Dorsey, bass; 
Zachary Alford, drums.
